"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-sport-paris-2024-postpones-triathlon-due-to-water-contamination-setback-as-seine-river-deemed-unsuitable-for-swimming-news-story-f1ccd4aed81819333d25ed58e0f1b4c1\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Olympic organisers have been hit by a major embarrassment as the men's triathlon has been postponed due to bacteria in the Seine River despite a controversial $2.4 billion clean-up.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2092823007393903e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympic Games have officially postponed the men's triathlon due to elevated levels of water contamination in the Seine River.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was made at 4.15am local time on Tuesday, less than four hours ahead of the scheduled start time of 8am (4pm AEST).\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While organisers were confident the water quality would improve by the morning, rigorous bacteriological analyses confirmed unsafe levels of enterococci and E. coli in the water.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An official statement declared: \\\"Following a meeting on water quality held on 30 July at 3.30am attended by Paris 2024\\u2026 decision has been made to postpone the men's triathlon event.\\\"\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2092823007393903e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The tests carried out in the Seine today revealed water quality levels that did not provide sufficient guarantees to allow the event to be held.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999980154826, \"rank\": 1.971947886438968e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will provide the athletes who are due to take part in the men's triathlon event with all information on its postponement, as well as real-time updates on the situation.\\\"\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The triathlon has now been delayed by a day.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"pic.twitter.com/4nlBRz2ibk  The rescheduling has come as a blow to both athletes and organisers, who have been grappling with the unpredictable water quality issues in recent days.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France had reportedly spent almost $2.5 billion on cleaning the Seine for the Olympics, causing Parisiennes tothreaten a poo protestfor perceived excessive expenses.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the river was thought to be adequately clean, recent heavy rains have significantly impacted water quality due to increased currents and raw sewage.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The final testing on Tuesday confirmed the levels of harmful bacteria exceeded safety thresholds.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the contingency plan, if swimming has been deemed unsafe on the rescheduled date on Wednesday, the event will have to be converted into a duathlon.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, with the postponement, organisers are hopeful the water quality could improve sufficiently by Wednesday morning.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This postponement marks the first time in Olympic triathlon history that a full triathlon has been rescheduled due to water contamination.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers hope to avoid a nightmare scenario like the 2023 World Cup in Sunderland, UK when collective gastroenteritis struck the event and more than 57 participants fell ill.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunderland_A.F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999277044962, \"rank\": 6.262021691800263e-08, \"text\": \"Sunderland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunderland_A.F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunderland_A.F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9989465216419826, \"rank\": 0.0010545893437601146, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 organising committee has assured that all necessary measures are being taken to address the contamination issues and prevent future disruptions.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2092823007393903e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several athletes have reacted to the news on social media and most appear to have taken to challenge in their stride.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tokyo 2020 champion Kristian Blummenfelt posted, \\\"No racing due to water quality\\\" while Paris 2024 favourite Alex Yee wrote \\\"We race tomorrow\\\".\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999994395239, \"rank\": 5.555647870845858e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristian_Blummenfelt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristian Blummenfelt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristian_Blummenfelt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristian_Blummenfelt\"}, {\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2092823007393903e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australians Matthew Hauser and Luke Willian are both set to compete for gold in the triathlon now scheduled to commence at 6.45pm on Wednesday, August 1 (AEST).\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2835, \"end\": 2849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hauser\", \"score\": 0.9999699347699281, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Hauser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hauser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hauser\"}, {\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel_of_Luke\", \"score\": 0.8553686387607562, \"rank\": 0.09959489848113906, \"text\": \"Luke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel_of_Luke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gospel_of_Luke\"}, {\"begin\": 2859, \"end\": 2866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willian_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"score\": 0.9223077835857433, \"rank\": 0.07766481500890002, \"text\": \"Willian\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willian_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willian_(footballer,_born_1988)\"}, {\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": []}]}"